r1320 | fabricecolin | 2008-08-04 22:15:56 +0800 (Mon, 04 Aug 2008) | 6 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/Collect/Makefile.am
   M /trunk/IndexSearch/FilterWrapper.h
   M /trunk/IndexSearch/IndexInterface.h
   M /trunk/IndexSearch/Makefile.am
