   M /trunk/IndexSearch/Xapian/XapianEngine.cpp

The QueryModifier would sometimes append n-1 bytes of the last CJKV character.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1291 | fabricecolin | 2008-07-06 21:03:23 +0800 (Sun, 06 Jul 2008) | 2 lines
