------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1183 | fabricecolin | 2008-02-21 22:35:29 +0800 (Thu, 21 Feb 2008) | 4 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/SQL/CrawlHistory.cpp
   M /trunk/SQL/CrawlHistory.h
