------------------------------------------------------------------------
r872 | fabricecolin | 2007-07-21 12:06:17 +0800 (Sat, 21 Jul 2007) | 5 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/Index/DBusXapianIndex.cpp
   M /trunk/Index/DBusXapianIndex.h
